nodes.text: Leevil pâté was a type of delicate paste that could be found on the planet Kubindi, which the Kubaz Garindan ezz Zavor consumed at one point in his life. While residing in Mos Eisley spaceport on the desert planet Tatooine in 0 BBY, Garindan reminisced about consuming leevil pâté and beesh legs while inhaling the various scents in the spaceport, as he had not tasted them in a long time.
Leevil pâté was mentioned in "The Secrets of Long Snoot," a short story written by Delilah S. Dawson and published in the 2017 anthology From a Certain Point of View.
